## 🧪 Example Usage

### ➕ Add a task
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/tasks \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"title":"Finish Resume", "completed":false}'

### Mark a Task as completed

curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/tasks/1/complete


### Validate the Blockchain

curl http://localhost:8080/tasks/validate



Why did I make this Mess?
I wanted to combine:

My learning in Java & Spring Boot

My interest in blockchain concepts

My understanding of multithreaded systems